        "timestamp": "2017-04-12 16:51:16.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-2\n\nThis is a case where the code looks \"wrong\", but is actually correct.  \nAt one point we had no relativePath in the parent tag of that root pom, and that causes a different compile error.  If that tag is omitted, the default of \"..\" is assumed ... and that relative path takes you not to odlparent, but rather to the sdnc-core pom.xml.  So, we added that relativePath to prevent that error.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
