        "timestamp": "2017-04-18 04:06:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nDan Timoney, It seems the issue exist when i do the clean build. kindly help. \n\nEarlier i have referred http://maven.apache.org/ref/3.0.3/maven-model/maven.html#class_parent tried to make this patch and makes to  refer odlparent from repository. \n\nI verified this fix, locally and it worked. Also ONAP Jobbuilder passed here. so IMHO, we could consider this change.",
